      <title>西南航空与激进主义者埃利奥特开始和解谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/southwest-activist-elliott-said-to-begin-settlement-discussions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 和西南航空公司 (Southwest Airlines Co.) 已开始讨论达成一项潜在和解协议，以避免发生争夺该航空公司董事会控制权的代理权之争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/southwest-activist-elliott-said-to-begin-settlement-discussions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 22:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
